# AI Generation Rules

Generation must be template-driven and section-based. Do not generate one giant unstructured document.

Each generated section should include section_id, title, body, source_facts_used, assumptions, and validation_notes.

Never invent certifications, customer names, case studies, market size, guaranteed SEO outcomes, or legal conclusions.
